title: adidas Skateboarding Krooked X adidas
description: adidas Skateboarding is pleased to present our collaboration with Krooked Skateboards. Join Mark Gonzales as he skates throughout New York City and explains some insights that include why he likes Manhattan, why he doesn’t like Brooklyn, and who Kev-lar is. The adidas Krooked pack is in stores now.
